au.edu.federation.alansley

Class Application

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.edu.federation.alansley.Application

  • public class Application
extends Object
    An example application to demonstrate the Caliko library in both 2D and 3D modes. Use up/down cursors to change between 2D/3D mode and left/right cursors to change demos. In 2D mode clicking using the left mouse button (LMB) changes the target location, and you can click and drag. In 3D mode, use W/S/A/D to move the camera and the mouse with LMB held down to look. See the README.txt for further documentation and controls.
    Version:
    0.9.9 - 09/01/2016
    Author:
    Al Lansley
